response.overview: Account holders can call on ☎️ +1-[864].336.8850 to request and initiate a refund at Kraken. Kraken dispute center at ☎️ +1-[864].336.8850 offers a straightforward process for refunds, but it's essential to understand the specific circumstances under which a refund is eligible. If a transaction error occurs contact ☎️ +1-[864].336.8850, Kraken may refund the transaction if it is due to a technical issue on their end, such as a network or system outage.
